_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/9dd30549e2d53aa966e6194d2b74be1f.webm?t=1736265623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Expand your kingdom with the help of quirky characters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/2b1499f13b329801a226dd03de164712.poster.avif?t=1736265623\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/2b1499f13b329801a226dd03de164712.webm?t=1736265623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Explore forgotten lairs and solve their mysteries to strengthen your reign, and to gain new powerful skills and perks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/2470dbfff18f6f08cfd25a269d25e9cb.poster.avif?t=1736265623\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/2470dbfff18f6f08cfd25a269d25e9cb.webm?t=1736265623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Make your villagers craft weapons and other equipment to defend your village from invading bandits. Will they be the only threat though?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/ff6a253ead080ea6e8fac3762c2e9c91.poster.avif?t=1736265623\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/ff6a253ead080ea6e8fac3762c2e9c91.webm?t=1736265623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581360/extras/5a610d08f767b74c280e1ab89fb202d9.webp?t=1736265623\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br><strong>The king has returned!</strong>",
